# Pipeline-in-progress: hold the new GLBs out of git while the 100-cell fetch
# runs, so each stop-hook trigger doesn't churn dozens of partial commits.
# Removed by the auto-deploy script once the pipeline completes.
public/meshes/activity/*.glb
!public/meshes/activity/864691136136406923.glb

